---
// No props needed for this component
import Logotipo7 from '../../public/Logotipo-07.png'
---

<footer class="relative overflow-hidden pt-20 pb-12 bg-gray-100">
  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 z-10">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
      <img src={Logotipo7.src} alt="SUBAXA Logo" class="h-16 sm:h-20 md:h-24 lg:h-28 object-contain">
    </div>

    <p class="text-gray-700 text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-xl max-w-5xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-center">
        Una plataforma para invertir, comprar casa o terreno fácil y seguro a un click, con un equipo de expertos que te acompañan en cada paso.
    </p>
    <address
      class="not-italic text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base text-center max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-1"
    >
      <p>
        <a href="mailto:info@subaxa.com" class="text-[var(--color-azul-electrico)] hover:underline"
          >info@subaxa.com</a
        >
        · <a href="tel:+50688211348" class="hover:underline">+506 8821-1348</a>
      </p>
      <p>San Carlos, Alajuela, Costa Rica</p>
    </address>
    <hr class="my-8 border-gray-400">
  </div>
  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 z-10 text-center text-gray-600 text-sm">
    © {new Date().getFullYear()} SUBAXA. Todos los derechos reservados.
  </div>
</footer>
